continued%20financially%20supporting%20Russia%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20has%20not%20tried%20to%20isolate%20it%20diplomatically%20%E2%80%94%20suggesting%20it%20has%20no%20desire%20to%20anger%20or%20confront%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20its%20efforts%20in%20the%20region%20undermine%20Russian%20dominance%2C%20and%20give%20China%20a%20relatively%20free%20run%20as%20Western%20countries%20are%20largely%20uninterested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22General%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Collective%20Security%20Treaty%20Organization%20(CSTO)%20Stanislav%20Zas%2C%20Armenian%20Prime%20Minister%20Nikol%20Pashinyan%2C%20Belarusian%20President%20Alexander%20Lukashenko%2C%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20Kazakh%20President%20Kassym-Jomart%20Tokayev%2C%20Kyrgyz%20President%20Sadyr%20Japarov%20and%20Tajik%20President%20Emomali%20Rakhmon%20pose%20for%20a%20picture%20during%20the%20CSTO%20summit%20at%20the%20Kremlin%20in%20Moscow%2C%20Russia%20in%20May%202022.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64539116b4a8cd00187ab716%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221331%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGeneral%20Secretary%20of%20the%20CSTO%20Stanislav%20Zas%2C%20Armenian%20Prime%20Minister%20Nikol%20Pashinyan%2C%20Belarusian%20President%20Alexander%20Lukashenko%2C%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20Kazakh%20President%20Kassym-Jomart%20Tokayev%2C%20Kyrgyz%20President%20Sadyr%20Japarov%20and%20Tajik%20President%20Emomali%20Rakhmon%20pose%20for%20a%20picture%20during%20the%20CSTO%20summit%20at%20the%20Kremlin%20in%20Moscow%2C%20Russia%20in%20May%202022.%3Cp%3ESputnik%2FAnton%20Novoderezhkin%2FPool%20via%20REUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20try%20to%20ease%20Russia's%20concerns%20about%20this%2C%20but%20the%20facts%20are%20the%20facts%3A%20that%20Chinese%20influence%20is%20growing%20and%20it's%20not%20growing%20in%20Central%20Asia%20at%20America's%20expense%2C%20it's%20growi