%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fhoward-marks-oaktree-capital-management-inflation-federal-reserve-companies-debt-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMany%20more%20companies%20are%20going%20to%20founder%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Oaktree%20Capital%20Management%20cofounder%20says%20in%20an%20upcoming%20interview%20with%20Bloomberg's%20David%20Rubenstein.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gglover%40insider.com%20(George%20Glover)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fhoward-marks-oaktree-capital-management-inflation-federal-reserve-companies-debt-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20miserable%2C%20euphoric%2C%20muddy%20escape%20from%20Burning%20Man%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20fiery%20orange%20and%20red%20scene%20is%20covered%20with%20bright%20tendrils%20of%20light%20swishing%20in%20and%20out%20the%20frame%2C%20with%20some%20exploding%20into%20spiky%20bulbs%20of%20light.%20Beneath%20the%20fiery%20cosmic%20scene%2C%20white%20silhouettes%20of%20dancing%20bodies%20swivel%20around%2C%20prancing%20in%20mud.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f8a2f1f1210f00198473df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDespite%20the%20food%20rationing%2C%20the%20mandatory%20pee%20bottles%2C%20and%20the%20malfunctioning%20infrastructure%2C%20Burners%20scraped%20the%20dirt%20off%20their%20shoes%20and%20got%20down.%3Cp%3EArantza%20Pena%20Popo%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20three%20o'clock%20in%20the%20morning%20on%20Sunday%2C%20as%20I%20sipped%20golden%20milk%20and%20watched%20a%20chess%20game%20besides%20a%20geodesic%20dome%20where%20revelers%20danced%20shoulder-to-shoulder%20beneath%20a%20propane%20jet%20shooting%20constant%20waves%20of%20flame%2C%20not%20long%20after%20an%20intimidatingly%20high-energy%20stranger%20had%20power-washed%20my%20friends%20and%20I's%20buttocks%20to%20the%20rhythm%20of%20thumping%20techno%2C%20I%20came%20to%20a%20conclusion%3A%20Burning%20Man%20wasn't%20completely%20ruined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20previous%20night%2C%20heavy%20rain%20had%20transformed%20the%20weeklong%20event's%20normally%20dusty%20environs%20into%20a%20muddy%20quagmire.%20Cell%20reception%20was%20non-existent%2C%20and%20rumors%20on%20the%20ground%20came%20in%20thick%20and%20fast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20roads%20were%20impossible%20to%20drive%20on%2C%20and%20a%20sheriff-enforced%20lockdown%20would%20keep%20us%20in%20the%20sludge%20for%20days%20after%20our%20intended%20departure%2C%20some%20said.%20FEMA%20was%20being%20called%20in%20to%20run%20disaster%20response%20%E2%80%94%20or%20was%20it%20the%20National%20Guard%20that%20was%20airdropping%20supplies%3F%20There%20was%20an%20Ebola%20outbreak.%20No%2C%20scratch%20that%2C%20E.coli%2C%20and%20all%2070%2C000-odd%20attendees%20were%20being%20secretly%20quarantined.%20Social%20media%20was%20having%20a%20field%20day%20turning%20Burning%20Man%20into%20the%20epicenter%20of%20schadenfreude%20and%20misinformation%2C%20the%20few%20people%20who%20managed%20to%20connect%20to%20the%20internet%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20of%20Burning%20Man%20was%20not%20quite%20so%20dire.%20Despite%20the%20food%20rationing%2C%20the%20mandatory%20pee%20bottles%2C%20and%20the%20malfunctioning%20infrastructure%2C%20Burners%2C%20as%20they%20call%20themselves%2C%20scraped%20the%20dirt%20off%20their%20shoes%20and%20got%20down.%20Late%20night%20raves%20were%20thrown.%20Gifts%20were%20given.%20Joy%20was%20shared.%20Some%20guests%20even%20got%20married.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20quasi-apocalyptic%20revelry%20came%20with%20a%20price.%20Not%20only%20was%20there%20the%20exorbitant%20entry%20fees%20and%20additional%20costs%20(and%20labor%2C%20and%20logistics)%20of%20building%20and%20maintaining%20a%20temporary%20city%20in%20the%20Nevada%20high%20desert%2C%20the%20flooding%20risked%20significant%20environmental%20damage%20to%20the%20event's%20pristine%20ecological%20setting.%20Litter%20and%20detritus%20spread%20across%20several%20square%20miles%2C%20submerged%20in%20muck%20%E2%80%94%20leaving%20a%20daunting%20job%20for%20the%20cleaning%20crews.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E2023%20was%20my%20first%20year%20at%20Burning%20Man.%20It%20was%20an%20extraordinary%20time%2C%20both%20euphoric%20and%20truly%20miserable.%20I%20came%20away%20from%20it%20with%20memories%2C%20mud%20on%20my%20face%2C%20and%20a%20question%3A%20At%20what%20point%20does%20the%20spectacle%20stop%20being%20worth%20the%20cost%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20wanted%20to%20go%20to%20Burning%20Man%20for%20years.%20What%20were%20they%20%3Cem%3Edoing%3C%2Fem%3E%20out%20there%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmerging%20out%20of%20the%20San%20Francisco%20art%20scene%20in%20the%20early%20nineties%2C%20Burning%20Man%20is%20an%20annual%20campout-slash-rave-slash-art-exhibition-slash-ephemeral-city%20that%20blooms%20and%20disappears%20in%20the%20Black%20Rock%20Desert%2C%20a%20bleak%20and%20inhospitable%20lake%20bed%20in%20northern%20Nevada.%20Originally%20a%20haven%20for%20performing%20artists%2C%20musicians%2C%20and%20those%20seeking%20alternative%20community%2C%20it%20has%20in%20more%20recent%20years%20become%20associated%20with%2C%20and%20purportedly%20corrupted%20by%2C%20Silicon%20Valley%20techies%2C%20influencers%2C%20and%20the%20rich.%20Even%20before%20this%20new%20guard%20arrived%2C%20it%20had%20a%20reputation%20for%20apocalyptic%20cosplay%20%E2%80%94%20with%20the%20setting%20known%20for%20its%20frequent%20alkaline%20dust%20storms%2C%20alternately%20freezing%20and%20scalding%20temperatures%2C%20and%20general%20hostility%20to%20almost%20all%20kinds%20of%20plant%20and%20animal%20life.%20I%20wanted%20to%20see%20that%20all%20for%20myself.%20The%20alleged%20cultural%20clash.%20The%20large-scale%20art%20installations.%20The%20commitment%20to%20a%20decommodified%20%26quot%3Bgifting%26quot%3B%20philosophy%2C%20in%20which%20no%20money%20is%20allowed%20to%20change%20hands.%20And%2C%20yeah%2C%20the%20sheer%20hedonism%20of%20a%20weeklong%20bacchanal%20in%20the%20desert.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20the%20stars%20finally%20aligned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20arrived%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20August%2030%2C%20and%20over%20my%20first%20two%20days%20I%20had%20a%20delightful%20time.%C2%A0%20Moments%20after%20checking%20in%2C%20an%20affable%20stranger%20tried%20to%20pour%20mescal%20down%20my%20throat%20as%20I%20erected%20my%20tent.%20We%20hopped%20on%20a%20shimmering%20two-story%20%26quot%3Bart%20car%26quot%3B%20(basically%2C%20a%20modified%20double-decker%20bus%20decked%20out%20with%20lights%20all%20over%20its%20exterior%20and%20a%20thumping%20sound%20system)%2C%20and%20rode%20it%20out%20to%20the%20central%20playa%2C%20a%20sea%20of%20lights%20and%20sounds%20stretching%20out%20before%20us.%20There%20were%20heaving%20dance-parties%20along%20the%20central%20street.%20Attendees%20strewn%20in%20LEDs%20and%20glowing%20wires%20for%20visibility%20against%20the%20night%2C%20an%20endless%20swarm%20of%20technicolor%20fireflies.%20And%20in%20the%20center%20of%20it%20all%2C%20the%20Man%2C%20a%20huge%20wooden%20effigy%20waiting%20to%20be%20ritually%20burned%20on%20Saturday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222445%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20crowd%20of%20dancers%20at%20Burning%20Man%20festival%2C%20surrounding%20a%20metal%20sculpture%20of%20an%20octopus%20shooting%20flames%20mounted%20on%20a%20car%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f8eed956f5190019fc86f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221833%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBurning%20Man%20was%20an%20uncomplicated%20delight%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0until%20the%20rains%20started.%3Cp%3EJULIE%20JAMMOT%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%C2%A0biked%20deep%20into%20the%20desert%20to%20check%20out%20some%20of%20the%20vast%20sculptures%20dotting%20the%20landscape%3A%20Train%20stations%2C%20monsters%2C%20butterflies%2C%20and%20genitalia.%20I%20was%20fed%20pie%20and%20%26quot%3BBetty%20Water%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20drink%20of%20uncertain%20origins%20and%20undeniable%20strength%20%E2%80%94%20by%20four%20drunk%20and%20bawdy%20waitresses%20all%20named%20Betty.%20I%20found%20an%20art%20car%20shaped%20like%20a%20tall%20sailing%20ship%20that%20could%20actually%20sail%20the%20desert%20winds.%20I%20was%20gifted%20clothes%2C%20books%2C%20meals%2C%20and%20trinkets%20by%20total%20strangers%2C%20and%20marveled%20at%20the%20novelty%20of%20an%20economic%20experiment%20divorced%20from%20commerce.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20on%20Friday%20night%2C%20the%20rain%20came%2C%20and%20our%20camp%20turned%20into%20a%20swamp.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20hours%2C%20the%20camp%20generator%20failed%2C%20and%20the%20fridges%20turned%20off.%20The%20water%20systems%20for%20washing%20up%20and%20showering%20broke%20down.%20The%20mud%20was%20ankle-deep%20in%20spots%2C%20alternately%20suctioning%20shoes%20right%20off%20your%20feet%20or%20lethally%20slippery.%20The%20roads%20were%20immediately%20impassable%2C%20Somme-like%20bogs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20tents%20were%20beneath%20a%20shade%20structure%20%E2%80%94%20metal%20poles%20and%20tarpaulin%20roofing%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0to%20protect%20them%20from%20the%20desert%20sun.%20Suddenly%20we%20had%20to%20push%20the%20water%20off%20the%20sides%20every%2015%20minutes%20before%20it%20pooled%20and%20made%20the%20entire%20structure%20collapse%20on%20us.%20As%20we%20patrolled%20the%20camp%2C%20some%20campmates%20huddled%20in%20the%20kitchen%20around%20a%20bluetooth%20speaker%2C%20wrapped%20in%20fur%20coats%20and%20trading%20drinks%20and%20stimulants%2C%20trying%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20morning%2C%20as%20the%20rain%20abated%2C%20we%20surveyed%20the%20damage.%20The%20mud%20clumped%20together%20instantly%2C%20turning%20shoes%20into%20increasingly%20heavy%20and%20unwieldy%20platform%20boots%20with%20each%20step.%20Some%20opted%20to%20wear%20plastic%20bags%20instead%2C%20or%20just%20go%20barefoot%20in%20the%20muck.%20It%20was%20clear%20we%20were%20stuck%20here%20for%20days%2C%20and%20the%20event%20organizers%20instructed%20attendees%20to%20start%20urinating%20in%20bottles%20to%20conserve%20space%20in%20the%20porta-potties.%20Our%20camp%20began%20rationing%20meals.%20Friends%20preemptively%20popped%20anti-diarrheal%20Imodium%20tablets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20there%20was%20the%20potential%20environmental%20damage.%20Far%20from%20civilization%2C%20the%20empty%20lake%20bed%20in%20the%20remote%20reaches%20of%20Northern%20Nevada%20makes%20the%20event's%20signature%20creativity%20and%20generosity%20feel%20magical%20%E2%80%94%20but%20also%20makes%20the%20risk%20of%20ecological%20impacts%20far%20higher.%20Attendees%20religiously%20patrol%20the%20site%20for%20%26quot%3Bmoop%26quot%3B%20(Matter%20Out%20Of%20Place%20%E2%80%94%20any%20litter%2C%20detritus%2C%20or%20human%20waste)%2C%20and%20crews%20spend%20weeks%20every%20year%20combing%20the%20site%20for%20any%20signs%20of%20Burning%20Man's%20impact%20on%20our%20burning%20planet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cq%3EWe%20found%20two%20lovers%20getting%20married%2C%20and%20joined%20them%20for%20their%20first%20dance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fq%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20restoration%20crew%20has%20its%20work%20cut%20out%20for%20it.%20In%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20rain%2C%20moop%20was%20everywhere.%20The%20porta-potties%20were%20surrounded%20by%20a%20halo%20of%20shredded%20toilet%20paper%20that%20clung%20to%20shoes.%20Flip-flops%2C%20bikes%2C%20clothes%2C%20scraps%20and%20other%20unidentifiable%20human-generated%20products%20were%20mashed%20into%20the%20ground%2C%20buried%20by%20up%20to%20a%20foot%20of%20fast-hardening%20brown%20ooze.%20Tarpaulins%20were%20shedding%20brightly-colored%20millimeter%20sized%20particulates%20into%20the%20standing%20water.%20Entire%20tents%20were%20abandoned%20by%20fleeing%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20picked%20up%20the%20moop%20we%20spotted%3B%20it%20didn't%20even%20scratch%20the%20surface.%20The%20detritus%20that%20remains%20behind%20is%20at%20risk%20of%20becoming%20a%20sedimentary%20testament%20to%20humanity's%20damage%20to%20the%20environment%20%E2%80%94%20even%20as%20human-caused%20climate%20change%20makes%20extreme%20weather%20events%20like%20Black%20Rock%20City's%20deluge%20of%202023%20all%20the%20more%20likely%20in%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20the%20floods%2C%20there%20was%20an%20uncomfortable%20tension%20to%20Burning%20Man.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20preaches%20%26quot%3Bradical%20inclusion%26quot%3B%20as%20one%20of%20its%20ten%20core%20guiding%20principles%2C%20and%20its%20uniqueness%20comes%20as%20a%20decommodified%20space%20where%20everything%20is%20free%20and%20participants%20will%20trip%20over%20themselves%20in%20their%20efforts%20to%20give%20you%20gifts%20and%20make%20your%20burn%20wonderful.%20But%20in%20practice%2C%20there%20are%20extraordinary%20hurdles%20to%20entry%3A%20Between%20tickets%20(%24595%20for%20general%20admission)%2C%20additional%20costs%20for%20vehicle%20passes%2C%20camp%20dues%2C%20food%2C%20water%2C%20survival%20equipment%2C%20goods%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20gifting%20economy%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%20a%20trip%20to%20Burning%20Man%20can%20easily%20stretch%20to%20thousands%20of%20dollars.%20There's%20also%20the%20logistical%20burden%20of%20figuring%20out%20what%20you%20need%2C%20how%20to%20physically%20survive%20in%20the%20remote%20desert%20for%20a%20week%2C%20connecting%20to%20a%20camp%20that%20can%20host%20you%2C%20and%20making%20your%20way%20there.%20It's%20a%20privileged%20event%20at%20the%20best%20of%20times%2C%20and%20now%20we%20were%20paying%20all%20this%20time%20and%20money%20to%20shelter%20in%20our%20tents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20spending%20a%20grim%20Saturday%20morning%20huddled%20in%20our%20tents%2C%20cranking%20a%20hand-powered%20radio%20for%20scraps%20of%20news%20on%20the%20festival's%20informational%20radio%20station%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20explore.%20Burning%20Man%20was%20diminished%2C%20but%20not%20extinguished.%20Art%20cars%20had%20either%20retreated%20to%20their%20home%20camps%20or%20become%20stuck%20in%20place%20where%20they'd%20been%20caught%20by%20the%20storm.%20Bikes%20were%20unusable.%20But%20the%20mud%20was%20passable%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20just%20barely%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0on%20foot.%20Over%20the%20next%20two%20days%2C%20between%20rain%20showers%2C%20we%20wandered%20from%20bar%20to%20camp%20to%20dance%20floor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20people%20at%20Burning%20Man%20festival%20in%20Nevada%20stand%20in%20mud%20and%20look%20at%20a%20double%20rainbow%20in%20the%20sky.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f8ec598a7840001961b2a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221950%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20mud%20diminished%20Burning%20Man%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20extinguish%20the%20event's%20spirit.%3Cp%3EJULIE%20JAMMOT%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20visited%20the%20Temple%2C%20a%20somber%20site%20of%20remembrance%20where%20people%20leave%20mementos%20to%20deceased%20friends%2C%20family%20members%2C%20lovers%2C%20and%20pets.%20We%20had%20wine%20and%20cheese%20at%20a%20friend's%20camp.%20We%20chilled%20at%20a%20M*A*S*H-themed%20tent-bar%2C%20where%20an%20aging%20stoner%20educated%20us%20on%20the%20finer%20points%20of%20different%20martini%20styles%20as%20reruns%20of%20the%20seventies%20sitcom%20played%20on%20a%20projector%20in%20the%20background.We%20watched%20fire-dancers%20practice%20their%20craft%20and%20learned%20to%20juggle%20(badly)%20on%20their%20dancefloor.%20We%20found%20two%20lovers%20getting%20married%2C%20and%20joined%20them%20for%20their%20first%20dance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwitter%20was%20full%20of%20titillating%20jokes%20about%20Burning%20Man's%20abrupt%20collapse%20into%20chaos%2C%20and%20the%20delicious%20schadenfreude%20of%20rich%20elites%20having%20a%20miserable%20time%20in%20the%20desert.%20But%20this%20wasn't%20entirely%20the%20case.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F09%2F03%2Fopinion%2Fcolumnists%2Fburning-man-rain-mud.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAs%20sociologist%20Zeynep%20Tufekci%20wrote%20in%20the%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20idea%20that%20disasters%20breed%20Lord%20of%20The%20Flies-like%20anarchy%20and%20violence%20has%20been%20proven%C2%A0%20false%20throughout%20history.%20Tufekci%20predicted%2C%20correctly%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20venture%20that%20many%20of%20the%20thousands%20trapped%20in%20the%20Nevada%20mud%20are%20mostly%20banding%20together%2C%20sharing%20shelter%2C%20food%20and%20water.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20Black%20Rock%20City%20citizens%20understandably%20checked%20out%2C%20and%20decided%20that%20the%20party%20was%20officially%20over%20for%20them.%20They%20stayed%20in%20their%20tents%2C%20or%20attempted%20to%20drive%20out%20through%20the%20swamp%20(not%20always%20successfully)%2C%20or%20hitchhiked%20back%20to%20civilization.%20But%20for%20many%20others%2C%20there%20was%20a%20zen%2C%20thoroughly%20Burner%20attitude%3A%20When%20life%20gives%20you%20a%20road%20full%20of%20impassable%20mud%2C%20you%20might%20as%20well%20use%20it%20to%20make%20DIY%20sculptures%20of%20penises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20burners%20love%20the%20%26quot%3Bdifficult%20burns%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20years%20defined%20by%20adversity%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0whether%20that's%20extreme%20heat%2C%20icy%20nights%2C%20constant%20dust%20storms%2C%20or%202023's%20flooding.%20They%20say%20it%20brings%20out%20the%20best%20in%20the%20community%2C%20tests%20people's%20commitment%20to%20the%20event%2C%20and%20helps%20them%20grow.%20But%20it%20comes%20at%20a%20high%20cost%20%E2%80%94%20both%20financially%2C%20and%20to%20a%20fragile%20desert%20ecology.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20I've%20had%20my%20fair%20share%20of%20survival-mode%20situations%20while%20backpacking%20and%20hiking%20around%20the%20American%20West.%20In%202020%2C%20we%20had%20to%20hike%20out%20twenty-plus%20miles%20to%20escape%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhundreds-stranded-hikers-campers-rescued-from-california-creek-fire-2020-9%5C%22%3Ethe%20Creek%20Fire%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20Ansel%20Adams%20Wilderness%2C%20a%20friend%20once%20had%20a%20seizure%20and%20had%20to%20be%20evacuated%20by%20helicopter%20from%20the%20trail.%20The%20bone-cold%20two-day%20rainstorm%20while%20we%20tried%20to%20hike%20the%20Teton%20Crest%20Trail.%20Lightning%2C%20bears%2C%20rattlesnakes%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20All%20that%20is%20to%20say%3A%20I%20love%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D0e40b83d7e8dacce290bc502e8c8a03fe35b76f8a9fa8afc6ce4ebfd868e1a81%26postID%3D64f75167909a7a425c5afec1%26postSlug%3Di-escaped-burning-man-mud-apocalypse-climate-change-2023-9%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.masterclass.com%252Farticles%252Ftype-2-fun%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BType%202%20Fun%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20pushing%20myself%20to%20my%20limit.%20And%20Burning%20Man's%20experience%20was%20extraordinary%20in%20a%20way%20many%20of%20its%20haters%20simply%20don't%20grasp.%20But%20it'll%20take%20me%20a%20while%20to%20decide%20if%20I%20need%20to%20do%20it%20again%20any%20time%20soon.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLiv_Boeree%2Fstatus%2F1698783890524000688%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDespite%20some%20burners'%20efforts%20to%20minimize%20accurate%20media%20reporting%20on%20the%20event%20as%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bclickbait%2C%26q