me%20if%20I%20placed%20a%20mobile%20order%2C%20to%20which%20I%20responded%20yes.%20After%20that%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-chains-like-white-castle-turn-to-voice-bots%3Finline-endstory-related-recommendations%3D%5C%22%3EAI%20voice%3C%2Fa%3E%20asked%20me%20to%20recite%20the%20order%20code.%20It%20registered%20the%20letters%20and%20numbers%20I%20read%2C%20and%20the%20order%20screen%20displayed%20a%20picture%20of%20my%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20McDonald's%20employee%20waved%20me%20past%20the%20pay%20window%2C%20since%20I%20had%20already%20paid%20through%20the%20app.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223023%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22McDonald's%20parking%20spot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f8c22656f5190019fc4e6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGrace%20Mayer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20got%20to%20the%20second%20window%2C%20my%20order%20wasn't%20ready%2C%20so%20an%20employee%20asked%20me%20to%20pull%20into%20one%20of%20the%20parking%20spots%20designated%20for%20drive-thru%20customers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMcDonald's%20beat%20Chick-fil-A's%20wait%20time%20by%20about%20six%20minutes.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223023%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22McDonald's%20bag%20of%20food%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f8c2328a78400019617a5f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGrace%20Mayer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20McDonald's%20employee%20delivered%20my%20order%20to%20my%20car%20window%20about%20four%20minutes%20after%20I%20first%20arrived%20at%20the%20ordering%20kiosk.%20But%20McDonald's%20was%20also%20serving%20far%20fewer%20customers%20in%20the%20drive-thru%20than%20the%20Chick-fil-A%20I%20visited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMcDonald's%20has%20been%20working%20on%20improving%20t