ryptocurrencies%20worth%20more%20than%20%24100%20million%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20has%20at%20least%2088%2C200%20crypto-millionaires%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20wealth%20report%20by%20London-based%20firm%20Henley%20%26amp%3B%20Partners.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20around%200.02%25%20of%20everyone%20who%20owns%20or%20trades%20in%20cryptocurrencies%2C%20which%20the%20report%20says%20is%20around%20425%20million%20people%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrypto-millionaires%20are%20defined%20as%20people%20who%20have%20at%20least%20%241%20million%20in%20cryptocurrency%20assets%2C%20per%20the%20firm's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.henleyglobal.com%2Fpublications%2Fcrypto-wealth-report%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECrypto%20Wealth%20Report%202023.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Nearly%20half%20of%20this%20crowd%20%E2%80%94%2040%2C500%20of%20them%20%E2%80%94%20own%20Bitcoin%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20at%20least%20182%20of%20crypto%20users%20have%20holdings%20of%20%24100%20million%20or%20more%20in%20cryptocurrencies%2C%20and%2022%20users%20own%20at%20least%20%241%20billion%20worth%20of%20cryptocurrencies%20each%2C%20according%20to%20Henley%20%26amp%3B%20Partners%2C%20which%20worked%20with%20South%20African%20wealth%20intelligence%20firm%20New%20World%20Wealth%20to%20collect%20its%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2088%2C200-strong%20crypto-millionaire%20crowd%20makes%20up%20only%20a%20small%20fraction%20of%20the%20world's%20total%20number%20of%20millionaires%2C%20of%20which%20there%20are%20more%20than%2020%20million%2C%20Andrew%20Amoils%2C%20head%20of%20research%20at%20New%20World%20Wealth%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20world's%20wealthy%20crypto%20users%20are%20starting%20to%20outnumber%20the%20number%20of%20high-net-worth%20individuals%20in%20entire%20countries%2C%20such%20as%20Russia%2C%C2%A0which%20has%2065%2C000%20millionaires%2C%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C