%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20and%20Justices%20J.B.%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%20asked%20the%C2%A0Manipur%20government%20and%20the%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20active%20in%20the%20state%20to%20file%20a%20status%20report%20on%20the%20recovery%20of%20arms%20made%20from%20%E2%80%9Call%20sources%E2%80%9D%2C%20PTI%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%20a%20status%20report%20be%20furnished%20to%20this%20court%20by%20the%20government.%20The%20report%20shall%20be%20made%20available%20only%20to%20this%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20further%20reported%20that%20the%20bench%20stressed%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20concerned%20with%20who%20looted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20looking%20at%20it%20as%20we%20have%20said%20repeatedly%20that%20we%20are%20not%20concerned%20with%20the%20source%20of%20the%20wrongdoing%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECJI%20Chandrachud%20reiterated%20that%20as%20was%20the%20case%20of%20human%20suffering%2C%20for%20disarmament%20also%20the%20court%20is%20not%20bothered%20at%20this%20stage%20about%20the%20source%20of%20the%20wrongdoing%20but%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20has%20to%20be%20accountability%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20dealing%20with%20this%20objectively.%20The%20state%20has%20to%20take%20action%20irrespective%20of%20the%20source%20where%20the%20illegal%20arms%20are%20situated%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CJI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELawyer%20objects%20to%20Manipur%20affidavit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fmanipur-violence-senior-advocate-meenakshi-arora-objects-state-government-affidavit-supreme-court%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20lawyer%20appearing%20for%20the%20all-woman%20judges%20committee%20appoin