an%3EInitially%2C%20he%20became%20known%20for%20performing%20a%20few%20miracles.%20His%20claims%20were%20questioned%20by%20some%20of%20the%20prominent%20latter-day%20reformists%20and%20writers%20at%20the%20time.%20He%20professed%20to%20be%20an%20avatar%20of%20Narayan%2C%20the%20God%2C%20and%20got%20rechristened%20as%20Swaminarayan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20showing%20Hanuman%20under%20his%20subservience%20enraged%20some%20people%2C%20the%20devotees%20of%20Swaminarayan%20found%20it%20in%20accordance%20with%20their%20belief%20of%20Swaminarayan%E2%80%99s%20supremacy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20bitter%20exchanges%20online%20and%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20things%20seem%20to%20have%20fallen%20into%20place%20with%20the%20hyperactive%20efforts%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20and%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP)%2C%20apparently%20with%20the%20top%20political%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20blessings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20would%20be%20interesting%20to%20note%20that%20the%20use%20of%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98sanatan%20dharma%E2%80%99%20instead%20of%20Hinduism%20is%20a%20comparatively%20recent%20coinage%20in%20mainstream%20media%20and%20online%20platforms.%20It%20is%20emphatically%20used%20to%20suggest%20some%20kind%20of%20ultimate%20form%20of%20Hinduism%2C%20arguably%20superior%20to%20Hindutva%2C%20that%20packs%20contemporary%20political%20messaging.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwhat-is-sanatana-dharma%5C%22%3EWhat%20Is%20Sanatana%20Dharma%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETake%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20controversy%20between%20Moraribapu%20and%20the%20Swaminarayan%20sect%20in%202019.%20Moraribapu%2C%20a%20celebrity%20performer%20of%20Ram%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekatha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeshgujarat.com%2F2019%2F09%2F06%2Fbaps-issues-strong-statement-against-morari-bapus-nilkanth-remark%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epassed%20a%20tongue-in-cheek%20comment%20on%20Sahajanand%20Swami%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20snowballed%20into%20a%20huge%20controversy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoraribapu%20was%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20massive%20trolling%2C%20a%20probable%20indication%20that%20he%20was%2C%20for%20some%20reason%2C%20out%20of%20favour%20with%20the%20big%20bosses.%20Otherwise%2C%20he%20professes%20humanitarian%20values%20and%20has%20been%20a%20long-time%20supporter%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20with%20equal%20ease.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20conflict%20was%20seen%20as%20destabilising%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20unity%E2%80%99%20as%20perceived%20by%20the%20RSS%20and%20related%20organisations.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20a%20compromise%20was%20reached%20between%20them%20and%20the%20Swaminarayan%20sect%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20VHP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fdocument%2F669668843%2FVHP-s-statement%5C%22%3Eissued%20a%20statement%20appealing%20for%20forgiveness%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20both%20sides.%20It%20was%20an%20unusual%20gesture%2C%20considering%20the%20VHP%E2%80%99s%20record%20in%20alleged%20cases%20of%20hurting%20religious%20sentiments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20noteworthy%20part%2C%20however%2C%20was%20the%20complete%20absence%20of%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98sanatan%20dharma%E2%80%99%20from%20its%20letter.%20It%20mentioned%20words%20like%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20dharma%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esamaj%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(society)%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98religion%2C%20culture%20and%20society%E2%80%99%20instead.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20particular%20instance%20of%20the%20mural%20at%20Salangpur%20involved%20one%20faction%20of%20the%20sect%2C%20namely%20the%20Vadtal%20faction%20(with%20its%20main%20centre%20at%20the%20central%20Gujarat%20town%20of%20Vadtal).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20more%20famous%20and%20more%20influential%20rival%20faction%2C%20BAPS%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20known%20for%20its%20sprawling%20Akshardham%20campuses%20at%20Delhi%20and%20Gandhinagar%2C%20and%20a%20record%20number%20of%20temples%20abroad%20%E2%80%93%20observed%20complete%20silence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RSS%20and%20VHP%20rushed%20to%20douse%20the%20fire%2C%20apparently%20for%20the%20unity%20of%20sanatan%20dharma.%20But%20the%20fact%20is%20the%20BJP%20cannot%20afford%20to%20displease%20either%20side.%20The%20Vadtal%20faction%20and%20the%20Swaminarayan%20sect%20at%20large%20wield%20huge%20clout%2C%20which%20could%20dent%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20political%20ease%20in%20the%20state.%20This%20also%20includes%20Patel%20power%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20crucial%20political%20factors%20in%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgujarat-assembly-elections-bjp-key-takeaways%5C%22%3EFour%20Key%20Takeaways%20From%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Historic%20Win%20in%20Gujarat%20Assembly%20Elections%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20pro-Swaminarayan%20pamphlet%20listed%20the%20social%20services%20of%20the%20sect.%20One%20of%20the%20points%20claimed%20is%20that%20the%20sect%20is%20the%20financial%20backbone%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20rotating%20huge%20amounts%20of%20money%20by%20arranging%20big%20functions%2C%20celebrations%2C%20erecting%20buildings%20etc.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20right-wing%20sentiment%20toward%20Hanuman%2C%20with%20his%20close%20relationship%20with%20Ram%20and%20Sita%2C%20obviously%20remains%20non-negotiable%20%E2%80%93%20with%20a%20notable%20exception%2C%20though.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20protectors%20of%20%E2%80%98sanatan%20dharma%E2%80%99%20were%20neither%20hostile%20nor%20did%20they%2