e%20done%20to%20fight%20climate%20change%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20blog%20post%20comes%20just%20a%20day%20ahead%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20where%20leaders%20from%20across%20the%20globe%20will%20gather%20to%20try%20and%20find%20solutions%20to%20problems%20ailing%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20wrote%20about%20how%20India's%20G20%20presidency%20has%20focused%20on%20a%20human-centric%20approach%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20rewards%20of%20globalisation%20reach%20the%20last%20mile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20One%20Earth%2C%20we%20are%20coming%20together%20to%20nurture%20our%20planet.%20As%20One%20Family%2C%20we%20support%20each%20other%20in%20the%20pursuit%20of%20growth.%20And%20we%20move%20together%20towards%20a%20shared%20future%20-%20One%20Future%20-%20which%20is%20an%20undeniable%20truth%20in%20these%20interconnected%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20pulled%20out%20all%20the%20stops%20for%20the%20G20%20Summit%20where%20world%20leaders%20will%20hold%20discussions%20on%20geopolitical%20tensions%2C%20economic%20slowdowns%2C%20and%20rising%20food%20and%20energy%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guest%20list%20includes%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20UK%20PM%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20Canada%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%2C%20and%20several%20other%20world%20leaders.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20India%20is%20hosting%20such%20a%20powerful%20group%20of%20leaders%20from%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20that%20this%20is%20not%20just%20a%20high-level%20diplomatic%20endeavour%20for%20India%2C%20but%20a%20way%20to%20showcase%20the%20country's%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20India%2C%20the%20G20%20Presidency%20is%20not%20merely%20a%20high-level%20diplomatic%20endeavour.%20As%20the%20Mother%20of%20Democracy%20and%20a%20model%20of%20diversity%2C%20we%20opened%20the%20doors%20of%20this%20experience%20to%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20accomplishing%20things%20at%20scale%20is%20a%20quality%20that%20is%20associated%20with%20India.%20The%20G20%20Presidency%20is%20no%20exception.%20It%20has%20become%20a%20people-driven%20movement.%20Over%20200%20meetings%20will%20have%20been%20organised%20in%2060%20Indian%20cities%20across%20the%20length%20and%20breadth%20of%20our%20nation%2C%20hosting%20nearly%20100%2C000%20delegates%20from%20125%20countries%20by%20the%20end%20of%20our%20term.%20No%20Presidency%20has%20ever%20encompassed%20such%20a%20vast%20and%20diverse%20geographical%20expanse%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694068200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F0rfl9m6o_narendra-modi-ani_625x300_07_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-blog-g20-summit-pm-modi-on-what-india-aims-to-achieve-with-grand-show-at-g20-summit-4367402%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22To%20combat%20climate%20change%2C%20the%20world%20needs%20to%20move%20away%20from%20a%20purely%20restrictive%20attitude%20on%20what%20should%20not%20be%20done%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-blog-g20-summit-pm-modi-on-what-india-aims-to-achieve-with-grand-show-at-g20-summit-4367402%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-blog-g20-summit-pm-modi-on-what-india-aims-to-achieve-with-grand-show-at-g20-summit-4367402%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-blog-g20-summit-pm-modi-on-what-india-aims-to-achieve-with-grand-show-at-g20-summit-4367402%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Joe%20Jonas%20chills%20with%20kids%20post%20filing%20divorce%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694068058000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22ht