k%20food%20and%20snacks%20and%20candy%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20one%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%20at%20all%20the%20frozen%20meals%20and%20ramen%20noodles.%20They%20are%20too%20lazy%20to%20work%20AND%20too%20lazy%20to%20cook.%20SMH%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20person%20commented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20others%20told%20Malik%20to%20have%20some%20empathy%20and%20consideration%20for%20the%20customer%2C%20who%20could%20be%20struggling%20financially.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20even%20afford%20that%20amount%20of%20food%2C%20there%20has%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20in%20the%20house.%20They%20probably%20been%20hungry%20since%20the%2015th.%20Food%20stamps%20are%20a%20blessing%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20one%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fshort-reads%2F2023%2F07%2F19%2Fwhat-the-data-says-about-food-stamps-in-the-u-s%2F%5C%22%3EPew%20Research%20Center%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2041.9%20million%20people%2C%20or%2012.5%25%20of%20the%20total%20US%20population%20use%20food%20stamps%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fns.usda.gov%2Fsnap%2Fsupplemental-nutrition-assistance-program%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupplemental%20Nutrition%20Assistant%20Program%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20SNAP%20for%20short.%20Households%20can%20rely%20on%20SNAP%20benefits%20to%20purchase%20necessities%20such%20as%20bread%20and%20vegetables%20but%20aren't%20allowed%20to%20purchase%20alcoholic%20beverages%20and%20health%20supplements%2C%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fns.usda.gov%2Fsnap%2Feligible-food-items%5C%22%3EUS%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Malik%20and%20Food%20Lion%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Insider%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcustomer-tried-buy-over-thousand-dollars-groceries-using-food-stamps-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694064265000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f941e28a7840001961cbdb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcustomer-tried-buy-over-thousand-dollars-groceries-using-food-stamps-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BYo%20they%20didn't%20even%20buy%20it%20and%20that's%20what%20making%20me%20even%20more%20mad%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20grocery%20store%20worker%20said%20in%20his%20TikTok%20post.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktan%40insider.com%20(Kwan%20Wei%20Kevin%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcustomer-tried-buy-over-thousand-dollars-groceries-using-food-stamps-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20Government%20'Neech'%3A%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister's%20Charge%20Against%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20accused%20the%20BJP%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20of%20being%20anti-poor%20and%20pro-capitalists.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20'neech'%20(despicable)%20and%20anti-humanity%20as%20they%20had%20denied%20supply%20of%20additional%20supply%20of%20rice%20to%20aid%20the%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20had%20sought%20rice%20from%20the%20Centre%20to%20provide%20an%20additional%205%20kgs%20to%20every%20beneficiary%20under%20the%20Anna%20Bhagya%20scheme%20of%20the%20State%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20the%20CM%20during%20my%20previous%20tenure%2C%20I%20was%20giving%20seven%20kg%20rice%20free%20but%20the%20previous%20BJP%20government%20reduced%20it%20to%20four%20kg%20and%20five%20kg.%20During%20the%20assembly%20election%2C%20I%20promised%20that%20we%20will%20give%20an%20additional%20five%20kg%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siddaramaiah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20they%20had%20also%20reached%20an%20agreement%20with%20the%20Food%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(FCI)%20to%20procure%20the%20rice.%20The%20FCI%20had%20assured%20the%20state%20government%20that%20it%20would%20provide%20the%20rice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20trust%20them%20(FCI)%20but%20the%20Centre%20denied%20us%20rice.%20We%20did%20not%20ask%20for%20rice%20for%20free.%20We%20were%20ready%20to%20pay%20for%20it.%20When%20we%20asked%20for%20rice%2C%20they%20agreed%20and%20then%20backtracked.%20You%20have%20to%20decide%20how%20%E2%80%98neech'%20(despicable)%20they%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20anti-poor.%20They%20don't%20have%20humanity%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siddaramaiah%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20Centre%20backtracking%20from%20supplying%20rice%20to%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20said%20that%20if%20free%20rice%20is%20given%20to%20the%20poor%20people%2C%20those%20states%20will%20go%20bankrupt.%20We%20told%20him%20that%20we%20will%20implement%20the%20five%20guarantees%20and%20we%20will%20not%20let%20the%20state%20go%20bankrupt.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CM%20also%20explained%20that%20out%20of%20the%20five%20poll%20guarantees%2C%20four%20have%20been%20implemented%20in%20the%20state.%20They%20are%20'Shakti'%20offering%20free%20bus%20rides%20to%20women%20in%20non-luxury%20government%20buses%2C%20'Gruha%20Lakshmi'%20providing%20Rs%202%2C000%20to%20the%20women%20head%20of%20families%2C%20'Gruha%20Jyothi'%20promising%20up%20to%20200%20units%20of%20free%20electricity%20to%20each%20household%20and%20'Anna%20Bhagya'%20offering%2010%20kg%20rice%20to%20BPL%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694064000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fetfgml5_siddaramaiah-ani_625x300_07_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww