esident%20Xi%20Jinping%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20who%20has%20not%20skipped%20any%20G20%20summits%20except%20for%20ones%20that%20came%20during%20times%20when%20COVID-19%20restrictions%20were%20in%20place.%20Last%20week%2C%20Russian%20president%20Vladimir%20Putin%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fvladimir-putin-will-not-attend-g20-summit-india%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eabsence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20New%20Delhi%20was%20also%20confirmed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faninews.in%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fgeneral-news%2Fthis-is-india-we-know-how-to-handle-the-world-external-affairs-minister-jaishankar20230906112202%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20news%20agency%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EANI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20at%20different%20G20%20summits%2C%20there%20have%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fg20-leader-dropouts-preemptive%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Evariable%20participation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20you%20had%20some%20occasions%20where%20you%20had%20a%20president%20or%20two%2C%20sometimes%20three%20who%20have%20not%20themselves%20come.%20But%20I%20do%20think%2C%20my%20sense%20from%20talking%20to%20the%20ministers%2C%20certainly%2C%20and%20I%20know%20the%20Sherpas%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20each%20other.%20They%20are%20right%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fno-delhi-declaration-west-g20-sherpas%5C%22%3Etrying%20to%20hammer%20out%20the%20final%20document%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20think%20everybody%20is%20coming%20with%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20seriousness%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fno-delhi-declaration-west-g20-sherpas%5C%22%3ENo%20Delhi%20Declaration%3F%20West%20Rejects%20India%E2%80%99s%20Compromise%20Text%20at%20G20%20Sherpas%20Meeting%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAsked%20whether%20Moscow%20and%20Beijing%20were%20%E2%80%9Cmiffed%E2%80%9D%20with%20India%2C%20Jaishankar%20denied%20it.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20no.%20I%20do%20not%20think%20it%20has%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20India.%20I%20think%20whatever%20decision%20they%20make%E2%80%A6I%20mean%20they%20would%20know%20best.%20But%20I%20would%20not%20at%20all%20see%20it%20the%20way%20you%20would%20suggest%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20minister%20also%20reiterated%20that%20the%20two%20leaders%E2%80%99%20absence%20will%20have%20any%20impact%20on%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20G20%20summit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20put%20it%20this%20way%2C%20the%20issues%20are%20there%20these%20are%20not%20issues%20that%20are%20this%20morning%20being%20taken%20up.%20I%20mean%20there%20is%20a%20whole%20gestation%20period%20of%20eight-nine%20months%2C%20where%20at%20different%20levels%20ministers%20or%20officials%20have%20tried%20to%20progress%20an%20issue.%20So%2C%20this%20is%20like%20a%20culmination%20you%20know%2C%20that%20is%20what%20this%20is%20really%20about.%20There%20are%20really%20about%2016-18%20processes%20which%20are%20all%20coming%20together%20to%20be%20stitched%20up%20together%20to%20produce%20a%20summit%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20reiterated%20that%20the%20efforts%20to%20get%20a%20consensus%20on%20a%20final%20declaration%20is%20still%20on.%20%E2%80%9CWell%2C%20we%20are%20negotiating%20right%20now%20as%20I%20said%20the%20negotiation%20is%20not%E2%80%A6%20The%20clock%20did%20not%20start%20ticking%20yesterday%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20G20%20sherpas%20are%20still%20discussing%20the%20text%20of%20the%20declaration%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20sign%20of%20compromise%20from%20either%20the%20West%20or%20Russia%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20issue.%20While%20both%20sides%20had%20agreed%20on%20a%20negotiated%20text%20at%20Bali%20last%20year%2C%20Russia%20and%20China%20had%20withdrawn%20their%20support%20soon%20after.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20joint%20statements%20have%20been%20issued%20after%20any%20of%20the%20G20%20ministerial%20meetings%20held%20so%20far%20under%20the%20Indian%20presidency.%20Instead%2C%20India%20has%20been%20issuing%20a%20document%20termed%20as%20%E2%80%9Cchair%E2%80%99s%20summary%20and%20outcome%20document%E2%80%9D%20to%20reflect%20that%20Russia%20and%20China%20do%20not%20want%20the%20G-20%20grouping%20to%20talk%20about%20Ukraine%20or%20other%20geo-political%20conflicts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20US%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Jake%20Sullivan%20also%20indicated%20that%20it%20will%20be%20difficult%20to%20release%20a%20Delhi%20declaration%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20summit%20on%20Sunday.%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20to%20get%20absolute%20consensus%20on%20a%20statement%20on%20Ukraine%20is%20challenging%20because%20you%E2%80%99ve%20got%20Russia%20seated%20at%20the%20table%2C%20albeit%20not%20at%20the%20leader%20level%20because%20Putin%20isn%E2%80%99t%20going%20to%20be%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fpress-briefings%2F2023%2F09%2F05%2Fpress-briefing-by-press-secretary-karine-jean-pierre-and-national-security-advisor-jake-sullivan-6%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20told%20reporters%20at%20a%20White%20House%20briefing%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694057220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29182852%2FF2mZGd1XEAAjRXY.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fjaishankar-g20-xi-jinping-vladimir-putin%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22No%20joint%20statements%20have%20been%20issued%20after%20any%20of%20the%20G20%20ministerial%20meetings%20held%20so%20far%20under%20the%20Indian%20presidency.%20Instead%2C%20India%20has%20been%20issuing%20a%20document%20called%20the%20'chair%E2%80%99s%20summary%20and%20outcome%20document.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fjaishankar-g20-xi-jinping-vladimir-putin%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22African%20Union's%20Full%20Membership%20Will%20Be%20Part%20of%20G20%20Outcome%20Document%2C%20Russia%20States%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07084105%2FScreenshot-2023-09-07-at-8.39.19.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20African%20Union%20will%20be%20admitted%20as%20a%20full%20member%20at%20the%2018%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20summit%20of%20the%20G20%2C%20Russia%20has%20confirmed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Russian%20G20%20sherpa%20Svetlana%20Lukash%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vedomosti.ru%2Fpolitics%2Farticles%2F2023%2F09%2F06%2F993621-afrikanskii-soyuz-stanet-chlenom-g20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%20a%20Russian%20business%20daily%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EVedomosti%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20provision%20for%20making%20the%20regional%20African%20organisation%20a%20full%20member%20will%20be%20included%20in%20the%20outcome%20document.%20Till%20now%2C%20the%20grouping%20had%20been%20made%20up%20of%2019%20countries%20and%20one%20regional%20organisation%2C%20the%20European%20Union%20(EU).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20annual%20summit%20of%20the%20grouping%20of%20the%2020%20large%20economies%20will%20be%20held%20over%20two%20days%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20September%209%20and%2010.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20AU%E2%80%99s%20membership%20of%20G20%20confirmed%2C%20the%20efforts%20will%20shift%20towards%20the%20competition%20for%20claiming%20credit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20prime%20minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20written%20to%20leaders%20of%20G20%20member%20states%20in%20June%20%E2%80%9Cto%20propose%20that%20the%20African%20Union%20be%20given%20full%20membership%20at%20the%20upcoming%20Delhi%20Summit%20of%20G20%2C%20as%20requested%20by%20them%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20India%20getting%20ready%20to%20project%20the%20AU%20membership%20as%20an%20achievement%20of%20its%20G20%20presidency%2C%20an%20article%20was%20published%20in%20a%20South%20African%20paper%20earlier%20this%20week%20with%20the%20authorship%20of%20Indian%20PM%20Modi.%20He%20highlighted%20that%20India%20had%20advocated%20for%20the%20inclusion%20of%20the%20regional%20group%20in%20the%20G20.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Russian%20official%20was%20also%20not%20behind%20in%20emphasising%20that%20Russia%20was%20among%20the%20first%20countries%20to%20support%20the%20AU%E2%80%99s%20application%2C%20which%20was%20submitted%20last%20year%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2FThe%2520most%2520pressing%2520issues%2520%25E2%2580%2594%2520climate%2520change%2C%2520pandemics%2C%2520security%2C%2520and%2520debt%2520%25E2%2580%2594%2520are%2520ones%2520that%2520both%2520affect%2520Africa%2520and%2520on%2520which%2520Africa%2520is%2520in%2520a%2520position%2520to%2520contribute%2520to%2520solutions.%2520Such%2520a%2520gap%2520in%2520African%2520representation%2520can%2520weaken%2520the%2520G-20%25E2%2580%2599s%2520credibility%2C%2520traction%2C%2520and%2520representativeness.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESenegalese%20President%20Macky%20Sall%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20during%20his%20chairmanship%20of%20the%20AU%20in%202022%2C%20urging%20G20%20leaders%20to%20grant%20the%20African%20bloc%20a%20permanent%20seat%20within%20the%20group.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CRussia%20believes%20that%20once%20implemented%2C%20the%20initiative%20of%20African%20nations%20would%20contribute%20to%20strengthening%20the%20positions%20of%20the%20majority%20of%20countries%20worldwide%20and%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lukash%20told%20the%20Russian%20media%20outlet.%20She%20also%20reminded%20that%20Russia%20had%20recently%20held%20a%20Russia-Africa%20summit%20in%20St%20Petersburg%20in%20July%2C%20where%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20had%20publicly%20voiced%20his%20support%20for%20the%20AU%20joining%20G20.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERussia%20had%20been%20wooing%20African%20countries%20and%20the%20Global%20South%20aggressively%2C%20as%20many%20of%20them%20had%20a%20more%20ambiguous%20position%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20and%20had%20abstained%20on%20UN%20resolutions%20related%20to%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20reported%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20Russia%20and%20China%2C%20EU%20was%20stepping%20up%20its%20outreach%20to%20African%20countries%20on%20the%20sideline%20of%20the%20G20%20summit.%20Terming%20it%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98mini%20summit%E2%80%99%2C%20top%20EU%20leadership%20and%20national%20leaders%20like%20German%20chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%20will%20hold%20a%20meeting%20on%20September%209%20with%20their%20counterpart%20from%20South%20Africa%2C%20Egypt%2C%20Nigeria%20and%20current%20AU%20chair%2C%20Comoros.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20gathering%20of%20EU%20and%20African%20leaders%20on%20Friday%20will%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-09-05%2Feu-seizes-on-putin-and-xi-s-g-20-summit-absence-to-engage-with-africa%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eendorse%20the%20entry%20of%20African%20Union%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20the%20G20%2C%20the%20n