%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-cop-caught-on-video-kissing-woman-and-climbing-into-police-car-suspended-4366949%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-cop-caught-on-video-kissing-woman-and-climbing-into-police-car-suspended-4366949%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Delhi%20Declaration%3F%20West%20Rejects%20India%E2%80%99s%20Compromise%20Text%20at%20G20%20Sherpas%20Meeting%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07082532%2FScreenshot-2023-09-07-at-8.25.26-AM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20There%20is%20growing%20pessimism%20about%20a%20unanimous%20leaders%20declaration%20being%20adopted%20by%20the%20G20%20at%20its%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20this%20weekend%2C%20after%20the%20G20%20Sherpas%2C%20who%20met%20at%20Nuh%20in%20Haryana%20from%20Monday%20to%20Wednesday%2C%20failed%20to%20reach%20a%20consensus.%20The%20United%20States%2C%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20the%20European%20Union%20and%20other%20Western%20nations%20refused%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Feu-official-says-indian-text-on-ukraine-does-not-go-far-enough%5C%22%3Eaccept%20the%20changes%20India%20proposed%20to%20the%20paragraph%20on%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20order%20to%20make%20it%20acceptable%20to%20Russia%20and%20China%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fjaishankar-discusses-g20-delhi-declaration-impasse-with-lavrov-as-sherpas-fail-to-reach-consensus-2676110%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Feu-official-says-indian-text-on-ukraine-does-not-go-far-enough%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported%20quoting%20a%20senior%20EU%20official%20who%20said%20that%20the%20text%20drafted%20by%20India%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20did%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20go%20far%20enough%E2%80%9D%20to%20be%20accepted%20by%20G7%20and%20EU%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExternal%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20met%20Russian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Sergey%20Lavrov%20in%20Jakarta%20on%20Wednesday%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20East%20Asia%20Summit%20to%20discuss%20the%20impasse%20about%20the%20declaration%20to%20be%20adopted%20by%20the%20G20%20leaders%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20The%20meeting%20was%20reportedly%20held%20to%20seek%20Lavrov%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20to%20end%20the%20impasse%2C%20which%20would%20give%20India%20the%20ignominious%20distinction%20of%20becoming%20the%20first%20country%2C%20under%20whose%20presidency%20a%20leaders%E2%80%99%20declaration%20could%20not%20be%20issued.%20In%20the%20year-long%20Indian%20presidency%2C%20there%20have%20been%20no%20joint%20communique%20from%20any%20ministerial%20or%20official%20meetings%20of%20the%20grouping%20that%20were%20held%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20unanimous%20declaration%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20minimum%20bar%20for%20any%20summit%20to%20be%20not%20declared%20a%20failure.%20With%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20choosing%20not%20to%20attend%20the%20summit%2C%20the%20event%20has%20already%20been%20robbed%20of%20much%20of%20its%20sheen.%20A%20failure%20to%20issue%20a%20declaration%20would%20reflect%20poorly%20on%20India%20globally%2C%20and%20especially%20on%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20has%20tried%20to%20showcase%20the%20routine%20rotational%20presidency%20of%20G20%20as%20a%20huge%20diplomatic%20achievement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBriefing%20journalists%20ahead%20of%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20New%20Delhi%20to%20attend%20the%20summit%2C%20Jake%20Sullivan%2C%20US%20National%20Security%20Advisor%2C%20told%20journalists%20in%20Washington%20DC%20that%20%E2%80%9Cto%20get%20absolute%20consensus%20on%20a%20statement%20on%20Ukraine%20is%20challenging%20because%20you%E2%80%99ve%20got%20Russia%20seated%20at%20the%20table%2C%20albeit%20not%20at%20the%20leader%20level%20because%20Putin%20isn%E2%80%99t%20going%20to%20be%20there.%E2%80%9D%20G20%20works%20on%20the%20principle%20of%20consensus%20and%20any%20member%20country%20has%20the%20right%20to%20exercise%20its%20veto%20over%20the%20final%20document.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sharp%20divisions%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%20between%20G7%20countries%20on%20one%20side%20and%20Russia%20and%20China%20on%20the%20other%20have%20made%20it%20impossible%20to%20reach%20a%20consensus.While%20the%20western%20countries%20have%20been%20insisting%20on%20the%20inclusion%20of%20text%20explicitly%20condemning%20Russia%CA%BCs%20military%20aggression%20against%20Ukraine%20in%20any%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Declaration%CA%BC%2C%20Beijing%20and%20Moscow%20have%20been%20opposing%20it.%20They%20argue%20that%20the%20G20%20is%20a%20forum%20meant%20to%20promote%20international%20economic%20cooperation%2C%20and%20not%20to%20discuss%20geopolitical%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20India%20took%20over%20the%20presidency%2C%20Beijing%20and%20Moscow%20have%20stridently%20opposed%20the%20Bali%20Declaration%CA%BCs%20two%20paragraphs%20on%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict.%20The%20G20%20Sherpas%20made%20a%20last-ditch%20attempt%20during%20a%20meeting%20in%20Nuh%20but%20failed%20to%20break%20the%20deadlock%20and%20rescue%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694055471000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07082532%2FScreenshot-2023-09-07-at-8.25.26-AM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fno-delhi-declaration-west-g20-sherpas%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20failure%20to%20issue%20a%20declaration%20would%20reflect%20poorly%20on%