20it%20is%20not%20going%20far%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20last%20time%20that%20any%20G20%20meeting%20had%20produced%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.g20.org%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fgtwenty%2Fgtwenty_new%2Fabout_g20%2Fprevious-summit-documents%2F2022-bali%2FG20%2520Bali%2520Leaders%2527%2520Declaration%2C%252015-16%2520November%25202022.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ejoint%20statement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20in%20Bali%20last%20year.%20Since%20then%2C%20India%20has%20been%20issuing%20%E2%80%98chair%E2%80%99s%20summary%20and%20outcome%20documents%E2%80%99%20at%20the%20conclusion%20of%20every%20ministerial%20meeting%20that%20recorded%20Russia%20and%20China%E2%80%99s%20objections%20in%20the%20footnotes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20G20%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20will%20be%20held%20on%20September%209%20and%2010%2C%20and%20will%20be%20attended%20by%20heads%20of%20state%20like%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhype-alone-cannot-sustain-the-g20-and-indias-presidency%5C%22%3EHype%20Alone%20Cannot%20Sustain%20the%20G20%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20Presidency%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20a%20joint%20statement%20was%20still%20possible%2C%20the%20EU%20official%20expressed%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20have%20a%20%5Bchair%E2%80%99s%20statement%5D%2C%20that%20will%20not%20be%20good%2C%20but%20that%20might%20be%20an%20outcome%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20EU%20official%20reiterated%20that%20the%20West%20cannot%20accept%20any%20language%20which%20dilutes%20the%20text%20that%20was%20used%20in%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20Bali%20to%20refer%20to%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20manage%2019%20against%20one%2C%20that%20would%20not%20be%20bad%20in%20a%20way.%20We%20want%20reflection%20of%20our%20position%20and%20what%20is%20important%20for%20us%2C%20and%20we%20are%20well-supported.%20It%20is%20more%20Russia%20that%20is%20isolated%20than%20G7%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20senior%20official%20noted%20that%20Ukraine%20will%20certainly%20dominate%20the%20discourse%20at%20the%20summit%2C%20since%20it%20would%20be%20on%20%E2%80%9Ceverybody%E2%80%99s%20mind%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20an%20illusion%20that%20you%20will%20just%20address%20economic%20topics.%20Of%20course%2C%20maybe%20you%20can%20say%20this%20for%20finance%20ministers%20and%20ministers%20and%20you%20have%20all%20those%20discussions.%20But%20when%20you%20have%20leaders%2C%20then%20it%20becomes%20more%20geopolitical.%20I%20think%20it%20is%20maybe%20the%20only%20forum%20where%20you%20have%20this%20plenary%20seating%20of%20leaders%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%2C%20friction%20is%20also%20expected%20on%20the%20issues%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20multilateral%20development%20banks%20and%20debt%20management.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20EU%20official%20mentioned%20that%20Russia%20and%20China%20have%20reservations%20about%20other%20aspects%20of%20the%20Bali%20declaration%20from%20last%20year%2C%20particularly%20regarding%20its%20language%20regarding%20the%20reduction%20of%20fossil%20fuel%20use%20and%20emissions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694024174000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04141303%2FFjHNMmeakAEkbxa.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Feu-official-says-indian-text-on-ukraine-does-not-go-far-enough%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20senior%20official%20noted%20that%20Ukraine%20wi