0%C2%A0The%20conflict%20situations%20exacerbate%20these%20challenges%2C%20making%20any%20data%20analytical%20exercise%20a%20difficult%20process.%20You%20can%20access%20the%20InfoSphere%20edition%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnesinfosphere.com%2F_files%2Fugd%2F85c814_66f6d1d42239442dacf25afb9974e058.pdf%5C%22%3Ehere.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intricate%20relationship%20between%20conflict%2C%20healthcare%20and%20community-based%20intervention%20calls%20for%20a%20need%20to%20analyse%20the%20role%20of%20external%20and%20internal%20factors%20that%20shape%20or%20influence%20a%20state%E2%80%99s%20healthcare%20landscape.%20Conflict%20situations%20exacerbate%20healthcare%20security.%20And%20it%20takes%20decades%20for%20community-based%20interventions%20to%20normalise%20health%20outcomes%20and%20build%20trust%20among%20a%20community%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20healthcare%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20current%20context%20of%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20crisis%2C%20Manipur%20serves%20as%20an%20ideal%20case%20study%20to%20examine%20the%20multifaceted%20impact%20of%20conflict%20situations%20on%20healthcare%20performance%20outcomes%20over%20time.%20By%20delving%20into%20economic%2C%20political%2C%20social%2C%20and%20environmental%20factors%2C%20as%20well%20as%20studying%20the%20role%20of%20local%20communities%20in%20peacebuilding%20processes%2C%20we%20can%20gain%20valuable%20insights%20into%20the%20complex%20interplay%20between%20conflict%20and%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECNES%E2%80%99s%20research%20team%20has%20spent%20the%20past%20three%20months%20closely%20studying%20the%20socio-political%20and%20socio-economic%20aspects%20of%20the%20conflict%20in%20Manipur.%20The%20lack%20of%20mobility%20and%20navigation%20options%20for%20external%20contingency%20response%20groups%20has%20made%20it%20difficult%20to%20provide%20relief-support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20such%20challenges%2C%20many%20people%20from%20the%20local%20community%20and%20social%20groups%20have%20consistently%20made%20efforts%20in%20ensuring%20better%20contingency%20response%2C%20providing%20access%20to%20basic%20amenities%2C%20such%20as%20healthcare%20security%20to%20the%20affected%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExternal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3Efactors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3Eshaping%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3Ehealthcare%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Ffigure%2FExternal-forces-affecting-health-care-delivery-Shi-and-Singh-2019_fig4_352954988%5C%22%3Eseveral%20factors%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20shape%20healthcare%20outcomes%20in%20a%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEconomic%20factors%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEconomic%20downturns%20can%20have%20detrimental%20effects%20on%20healthcare%20access.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20an%20economy%2C%20where%20medical%20costs%20are%20high%20and%20even%20unaffordable%20for%20many%2C%20the%20slowdown%20can%20often%20lead%20families%20to%20delay%20or%20even%20forgo%20necessary%20healthcare.%20In%20Manipur%2C%20the%20existing%20economic%20challenges%20exacerbate%20healthcare%20access%20issues%2C%20disproportionately%20affecting%20the%20vulnerable%20populations%20who%20struggle%20to%20cope%20with%20both%20conflict-related%20displacement%20and%20financial%20strain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20factors%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20stable%20political%20environment%20is%20conducive%20to%20a%20well-functioning%20healthcare%20sector.%20Conversely%2C%20political%20instability%20can%20have%20a%20detrimental%20impact%20on%20healthcare%20services%20and%20accessibility.%20In%20Manipur%2C%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20conflict%20disrupts%20healthcare%20services%20and%20impedes%20healthcare%20workers%E2%80%99%20ability%20to%20reach%20patients%2C%20resulting%20in%20limited%20access%20to%20chronic%20disease%20treatments%20and%20general%20healthcare%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESocial%20factors%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESociocultural%20factors%2C%20including%20cultural%20beliefs%2C%20education%20levels%2C%20and%20openness%20to%20modern%20treatments%2C%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20shaping%20healthcare%20utilisation%20patterns.%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20diverse%20cultural%20landscape%20influences%20healthcare%20practices%2C%20as%20certain%20communities%20may%20hold%20strong%20beliefs%20in%20traditional%20medicine%2C%20leading%20them%20to%20prioritise%20these%20practices%20over%20modern%20healthcare%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnvironmental%20factors%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEnvironmental%20factors%20such%20as%20air%20pollution%20and%20water%20contamination%20can%20significantly%20affect%20public%20health%20outcomes.%20In%20Manipur%2C%20the%20restricted%20mobility%20caused%20by%20the%20conflict%20presents%20challenges%20in%20coordinating%20effective%20healthcare%20responses%2C%20leaving%20communities%20vulnerable%20to%20various%20health%20risks%2C%20including%20exposure%20to%20pollution-related%20health%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EResource%20availability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAdequate%20resources%2C%20including%20skilled%20labour%2C%20sufficient%20funds%2C%20and%20proper%20medical%20equipment%2C%20are%20critical%20for%20ensuring%20quality%20healthcare.%20In%20Manipur%2C%20shortages%20of%20trained%20medical%20personnel%20lead%20to%20poor%20healthcare%20quality.%20This%20could%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20public%20health%20centres.%20This%20scarcity%20of%20resources%20underscores%20the%20importance%20of%20addressing%20resource%20limitations%20in%20healthcare%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20conflict%E2%80%99s%20impact%20on%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20healthcare%20system%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20ethnic%20conflict%20in%20Manipur%20has%20far-reaching%20implications%20for%20its%20healthcare%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict-driven%20displacement%20of%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-burden-of-conflict-on-manipur-healthcare-an-evolving-humanitarian-crisis%23read-more%5C%22%3E50%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-burden-of-conflict-on-manipur-healthcare-an-evolving-humanitarian-crisis%23read-more%5C%22%3Epeople%3C%2Fa%3E%20places%20immense%20strain%20on%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20healthcare%20system.%20Many%20healthcare%20workers%20have%20been%20injured%20due%20to%20attacks%20on%20healthcare%20facilities%2C%20leading%20to%20disruptions%20in%20essential%20healthcare%20services.%20The%20conflict%E2%80%99s%20resultant%20disruption%20has%20particularly%20dire%20consequences%20for%20those%20in%20need%20of%20chronic%20disease%20management%20and%20general%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%20has%20also%20adversely%20affected%20access%20to%20mental%20healthcare.%20The%20restricted%20movement%20due%20to%20the%20crisis%20has%20significantly%20reduced%20people%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20seek%20and%20access%20mental%20health%20services.%20Given%20the%20psychological%20toll%20of%20any%20crisis%2C%20the%20reduced%20availability%20of%20mental%20health%20support%20is%20a%20concerning%20aspect%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20current%20healthcare%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20navigational%20challenges%20and%20restricted%20mobility%20have%20impeded%20effective%20healthcare%20responses.%20This%20situation%20not%20only%20hampers%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20coordinate%20healthcare%20efforts%20but%20also%20exacerbates%20the%20existing%20strain%20on%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20healthcare%20infrastructure%2C%20leading%20to%20an%20overreliance%20on%20the%20already%20stretched%20medical%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChallenges%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20healthcare%20system%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%E2%80%99s%20healthcare%20system%20faces%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fruralindiaonline.org%2Fen%2Flibrary%2Fresource%2Fnational-family-health-survey-nfhs-4-2015-16-india%2F%5C%22%3Emultitude%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fruralindiaonline.org%2Fen%2Flibrary%2Fresource%2Fnational-family-health-survey-nfhs-4-2015-16-india%2F%5C%22%3Eof%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fruralindiaonline.org%2Fen%2Flibrary%2Fresource%2Fnational-family-health-survey-nfhs-4-2015-16-india%2F%5C%22%3Echallenges%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20impact%20its%20ability%20to%20effectively%20respond%20to%20conflicts%20and%20ensure%20healthcare%20security%20for%20its%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisparities%20in%20access%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20disparities%20in%20access%20to%20healthcare%20are%20more%20pronounced%20in%20remote%20and%20hilly%20regions%2C%20where%20the%20challenging%20terrain%20and%20inadequate%20infrastructure%20hinder%20access%20to%20healthcare%20services.%20These%20challenges%20are%20exacerbated%20in%20tribal%20areas%2C%20where%20lower%20percentages%20of%20assisted%20births%20by%20medical%20professionals%20contribute%20to%20greater%20healthcare%20disparities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESelf-medication%20and%20traditional%20practices%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20qualified%20healthcare%20practitioners%20often%20leads%20to%20self-medication%20and%20reliance%20on%20traditional%20practices.%20This%20practice%20poses%20considerable%20risks%20to%20patients%E2%80%99%20well-being%2C%20as%20incorrect%20diagnosis%20and%20treatment%20can%20lead%20to%20adverse%20health%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDual%20practice%20of%20doctors%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20dual%20practice%20of%20doctors%2C%20serving%20both%20in%20government%20and%20private%20hospitals%2C%20has%20implications%20for%20healthcare%20quality.%20This%20practice%20leads%20to%20shortages%20of%20doctors%20in%20government%20hospitals%2C%20impacting%20the%20level%20of%20care%20provided.%20This%20dual%20practice%20also%20raises%20questions%20ab