net%2FGP.asp%3Fsrc%3D8..230623.jun23%5C%22%3EPangal%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20Kuki%20communities%20have%20demonstrated%20solidarity%20through%20torch%20rallies%20and%20human%20chains%2C%20emphasising%20the%20importance%20of%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fjenkinstony_the-christian-forum-dimapur-visits-manipur-activity-7091039961411371008-sxso%2F%5C%22%3EChristian%20Forum%20Dimapur%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20embraced%20an%20inclusive%20approach%20by%20collaborating%20with%20various%20communities%2C%20showcasing%20the%20potential%20of%20community-driven%20initiatives%20in%20promoting%20peace%20and%20harmony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETransitioning%20from%20classical%20to%20resilience%20humanitarianism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paradigm%20shift%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjhumanitarianaction.springeropen.com%2Farticles%2F10.1186%2Fs41018-018-0043-6%5C%22%3EClassical%20Dunantist%20Humanitarianism%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Resilience%20Humanitarianism%20is%20evident%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20context.%20This%20transition%20signifies%20the%20move%20from%20providing%20immediate%20relief%20to%20building%20long-term%20community%20resilience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20integration%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Finternal-displacement-panel%2Fsites%2Fwww.un.org.internal-displacement-panel%2Ffiles%2Fidrp_hlp_submission_ws3_triple_nexus.pdf%5C%22%3ETriple%20Nexus%20Approach%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20encompassing%20humanitarian%20development%20and%20peacebuilding%20efforts%2C%20emphasises%20a%20comprehensive%20approach%20to%20conflict%20mitigation%20and%20crisis%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20shift%20is%20supported%20by%20local%20community%20involvement%2C%20as%20seen%20in%20the%20initiatives%20undertaken%20by%20different%20communities%20in%20Manipur.%20The%20emphasis%20on%20resilience%20acknowledges%20the%20interconnectedness%20of%20healthcare%2C%20peace%2C%20and%20development%2C%20promoting%20sustainable%20solutions%20that%20address%20the%20root%20causes%20of%20conflicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderstanding%20the%20external%20factors%20that%20shape%20healthcare%20outcomes%20during%20conflicts%20is%20crucial%20for%20crafting%20effective%20interventions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%E2%80%99s%20case%20underscores%20the%20need%20to%20address%20economic%20challenges%2C%20ensure%20a%20stable%20political%20environment%2C%20consider%20sociocultural%20dynamics%2C%20and%20allocate%20resources%20effectively.%20The%20active%20participation%20of%20local%20communities%20in%20peacebuilding%20and%20healthcare%20initiatives%20signifies%20the%20transition%20towards%20resilience-based%20approaches%2C%20fostering%20unity%2C%20dialogue%2C%20and%20long-term%20stability.%20By%20recognising%20the%20interdependence%20of%20healthcare%2C%20peace%2C%20and%20development%2C%20Manipur%20is%20charting%20a%20path%20towards%20a%20more%20inclusive%20and%20sustainable%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20one%20needs%20is%20more%20ground%20data%20for%20allowing%20local%20internal%20and%20external%20actors%20to%20provide%20immediate%20assistance%20and%20relief%20to%20the%20affected%20groups%20and%20displaced%20communities.%20Designing%20responses%20also%20requires%20data%2Fevidence%20based%20on%20local%20insights%20and%20regular%20information%20flows.%20Peacebuilding%20efforts%20take%20time%2C%20and%20what%20takes%20even%20longer%20is%20a%20process%20of%20trust-building%20among%20those%20who%20have%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20conflict.%20A%20lot%20more%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20in%20this%20regard%20and%20so%20far%20whatever%20little%20evidence%20we%20have%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20state%20doing%20so%20%E2%80%93%20is%20quite%20underwhelming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDeepanshu%20Mohan%C2%A0is%20Professor%20of%20Economics%20and%20Director%2C%20Centre%20for%20New%20Economics%20Studies%20(CNES)%2C%20Jindal%20School%20of%20Liberal%20Arts%20and%20Humanities%2C%20O.P.%20J