.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20selling%20fresh%20and%20sun-dried%20mushrooms%2C%20its%20spawns%20and%20other%20unique%20products%20like%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F267276%2Fmushroom-farm-punjab-randhawa-success-earn-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emushroom%C2%A0%3Cem%3Epapad%3C%2Fem%3Es%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20pickles%2C%20biscuits%2C%20and%20protein%20powder%2C%20Nidhi%20manages%20to%20earn%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimultaneously%2C%20she%20also%20teaches%20biology%20to%20Class%2011%20and%2012%20students.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20quit%20teaching%20because%20I%20am%20passionate%20about%20it.%20My%20husband%20always%20motivated%20me%20in%20this%20journey.%20There%20have%20been%20times%20when%20I%20lost%20hope%2C%20but%20he%20always%20encouraged%20me.%20He%20even%20quit%20his%20job%20at%20Reliance%20as%20a%20branch%20manager%20to%20support%20me%20in%20marketing%20and%20expanding%20the%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20husband%2C%20Sanjay%20Katare%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20from%20scratch.%20We%20knew%20that%20these%20mushrooms%20were%20in%20great%20demand%20by%20pharmaceutical%20companies%2C%20but%20we%20did%20not%20know%20how%20to%20market%20the%20products%20to%20the%20right%20people.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20goes%20on%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20I%20even%20went%20door-to-door%20to%20sell%20our%20oyster%20mushrooms%20to%20traders%20in%20the%20Delhi%20market.%20Today%2C%20we%20sell%20our%20products%20across%20India%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20Pune%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Surat%20and%20Kutch%20among%20other%20cities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20his%20decision%20to%20quit%20the%20job%20to%20support%20his%20wife%E2%80%99s%20business%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20very%20risky%20decisio