%5C%22%3Ehealthier%20alternative%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20refined%20oils%2C%20he%20started%20Gramiyaa%20in%202017%20with%20college%20friends%20Mohamed%20Yaseen%20and%20Naveen%20Rajamaran.%20The%20trio%20sells%20at%20least%2050%2C000%20litres%20of%20minimally%20processed%20cold-pressed%20oils%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBringing%20wood-pressed%20oil%20back%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20graduation%20in%20robotics%20and%20automation%20in%202015%2C%20Sibi%20got%20into%20the%20family%20business%20of%20automobile%20dealerships%20and%20running%20restaurants.%20It%20was%20when%20he%20wanted%20to%20purchase%20oils%20in%20bulk%20for%20his%20restaurant%20business%20that%20he%20realised%20the%20heavy%20usage%20of%20chemical%20solvents%20and%20adulterations%20in%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20saw%20how%20oils%20were%20adulterated%20with%20cheaper%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F213817%2Fpalm-oil-healthy-alternatives-vegetable-oil-planet-damage-deforestation-climate-change-lifestyle-char01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epalm%20oil%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20cotton%20seed%20oil.%20That%20is%20when%20I%20remembered%20how%20my%20%3Cem%3Ethatha%20%3C%2Fem%3Eused%20to%20make%20good-quality%20oils%20in%20a%20stone%20mill.%20These%20were%20minimally%20processed%2C%20preservative-free%2C%20and%20flavourful%20as%20well.%20I%20missed%20the%20memories%20and%20wanted%20to%20revive%20the%20business%20for%20good%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20oils%20are%20manufactured%20at%20Gramiyaa%2C%20Yaseen%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20we%20get%20only%20low%20moisture%20seeds%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Kerala.%20Usually%2C%20companies%20get%20cheaper%20seeds%20with%20more%20moisture%20content%20and%20roast%20them%20before%20extraction.%20We%20do%20not%20