h%2C%20Dwarka%2C%20Jagannath%20Puri%20and%20Rameswaram%20%E2%80%94%20Yati%20is%20excited%20about%20what%20is%20before%20them.%20He%20says%20that%20it%20will%20take%20him%20another%2010%20months%20to%20complete%20his%20Chardham%20expedition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20explore%20further%20down%20south%20and%20see%20the%20variety%20of%20cultures%20there.%20I%20have%20enjoyed%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Eevery%20bit%20of%20my%20walk%20so%20far%20and%20Buttercup%2C%20too%2C%20has%20been%20very%20enthusiastic%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20an%20anecdote%20when%20he%20was%20met%20with%20kindness%20on%20the%20road%2C%20Yati%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20warned%20about%20language%20barriers%20in%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20the%20country.%20However%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20learn%20Telugu%20when%20I%20entered%20Andhra.%20In%20my%20broken%20Telugu%20in%20Visakhapatnam%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20explain%20to%20a%20shopkeeper%20how%20my%20parcel%20would%20be%20delivered%20here.%20He%20laughed%20and%20uttered%20broken%20Hindi%20so%20that%20it%20was%20easier%20for%20me%20to%20understand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20he%20manages%20his%20travel%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-2-1693402469.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yati%20has%20travelled%20to%20states%20like%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Goa%20etc%20on%20foot.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-2-1693402469.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-2-1693402469-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-2-1693402469-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-2-1693402469-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-2-1693402469-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-328592%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EYati%20has%20travelled%20to%20states%20like%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Goa%20etc.%20on%20foot.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Yati%20Gaur%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20challenges%20that%20he%20faces%20while%20on%20his%20walking%20expeditions%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20in%20India%20have%20largely%20been%20wonderful%20and%20helpful%20to%20me.%20The%20only%20issue%20that%20I%20face%20sometimes%20is%20finding%20pet-friendly%20hotels%20to%20stay%20in.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%20the%20hotels%20I%20book%20say%20that%20they%20are%20pet-friendly%20but%20end%20up%20asking%20me%20to%20keep%20Buttercup%20outside%20the%20room.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20it%20becomes%20a%20little%20difficult%20to%20find%20another%20hotel.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20how%20technology%20is%20his%20other%20companion%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%2C%20Google%20Maps%20does%20not%20work%20or%20show%20the%20wrong%20distance.%20Even%20if%20the%20map%20shows%20fewer%20kilometres%2C%20it%20can%20become%20at%20least%20a%20half%20hour%20more%20of%20walking.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20try%20to%20travel%20as%20light%20as%20I%20can%20with%20minimal%20clothing%20and%20essentials%20like%20medicines%20and%20toiletries.%20I%20also%20try%20to%20avoid%20using%20gadgets%20while%20walking%20to%20save%20as%20much%20battery%20as%20I%20can%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.c