%20network%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20helped%20boost%20the%20income%20of%20scrap%20dealers%20up%20to%2036%20percent.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20clean%20tech%20company%20that%20provides%20digital%20software-driven%20solutions%20for%20circulation%20among%20bulk%20waste-generating%20companies%2C%20scrap%20dealers%2C%20and%20recyclers%2C%20Recykal%20has%20set%20out%20to%20reduce%20waste%20accumulation%20in%20the%20oceans%20and%20provide%20a%20better%20life%20for%20the%20people%20involved%20in%20this%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDisrupting%20the%20informal%20waste%20supply%20chain%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20month%2C%20Rajvardhan%20is%20able%20to%20sell%20150-200%20tonnes%20of%20waste%20like%20PET%20bottles%20through%20the%20Recykal%20app.%20%E2%80%9CPreviously%2C%20I%20would%20manage%20to%20earn%20Rs%2015%2C000%2C%20but%20today%2C%20my%20income%20has%20doubled.%20I%20never%20knew%20I%20could%20expand%20my%20business%20using%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rajvardhan%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20scrap%20dealer%20since%20the%20age%20of%2015%20and%20never%20went%20to%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhay%20Deshpande%2C%20one%20of%20the%20founders%20and%20a%20graduate%20in%20computer%20science%2C%20says%20that%20he%20has%20always%20been%20inclined%20towards%20entrepreneurship.%20In%202015%2C%20after%20establishing%20two%20companies%20%E2%80%93%20Malamall%20and%20Martjack%20%E2%80%93%20the%2052-year-old%20wanted%20to%20take%20a%20six-month%20break%20from%20his%20entrepreneurial%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20I%20had%20a%20tough%20professional%20journey%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20take%20a%20break%20and%20spend%20time%20with%20my%20family.%20But%20on%20the%20sixth%20day%2C%20I%20realised%20it%20was%20difficult%20for%20an%20entrepreneur%20to%20sit%20and%20relax%20at%20home%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20my%20family%20felt%20their%20privacy%20was%20being%20disturbed%20as%20I%20would%20keep%20aski