0blame%20for%20her%20condition.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20society%2C%20especially%20in%20small%20towns%20in%20India%2C%20only%20blames%20the%20victim.%20While%20the%20pain%20was%20unbearable%2C%20it%20was%20the%20comments%20from%20people%20that%20left%20me%20shaken.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20would%20shame%20me%20and%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98It%E2%80%99s%20the%20way%20you%20dress%3B%20you%20asked%20for%20it!%E2%80%99%20After%20a%20year%2C%20the%20scars%20started%20to%20fade%2C%20but%20the%20incident%20wrecked%20my%20self-confidence%20and%20left%20me%20very%20scared.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20support%20from%20loved%20ones%2C%20Devanshi%20regained%20her%20health%2C%20but%20her%20fear%20of%20public%20shame%20stayed%20with%20her.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20so%20scared%20of%20being%20shamed%20that%20I%20did%20not%20raise%20my%20voice%20when%20a%20family%20friend%20tried%20to%20molest%20me.%20I%20escaped%20his%20first%20attempt%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20he%20would%20come%20back%2C%20and%20he%20did.%20I%20was%20so%20afraid%20that%20I%20could%20not%20even%20talk%20to%20my%20mother%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20broke%20my%20silence%20once%20I%20realised%20that%20this%20was%20never%20going%20to%20stop.%20I%20told%20my%20mom%20and%20my%20family%20dealt%20with%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20incident%20helped%20me%20realise%20that%20silence%20never%20helps.%20I%20began%20to%20think%20that%20as%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20speak%20up%2C%20there%20must%20be%20many%20others%20like%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20beacon%20of%20hope%20for%20others%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai-7-1692973048.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Devanshi%20has%20helped%20t