D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20welfare%20society%20works%20with%20victims%20of%20sexual%20and%20physical%20abuse%20and%20gives%20them%20free%20legal%20help.%20Besides%2C%20Devanshi%20also%20gives%20free%20counselling%20to%20them.%20%E2%80%9CGetting%20proper%20counselling%20and%20knowing%20the%20next%20steps%20is%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20healing%20after%20abuse.%20The%20people%20who%20come%20to%20me%20are%20usually%20very%20scared%20and%20unsure%20of%20what%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20volunteers%20and%20I%20help%20them%20gain%20their%20lost%20confidence%20and%20also%20help%20them%20legally%20every%20step%20of%20the%20way.%20The%20justice%20system%20is%20not%20as%20efficient%20as%20we%20would%20like%20it%20to%20be%2C%20but%20the%20important%20thing%20is%20that%20we%20take%20the%20first%20step%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevanshi%20accompanies%20the%20victims%20to%20the%20police%20station%2C%20court%2C%20and%20wherever%20else%20is%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20NGO%20in%20Bareilly%20has%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20and%20many%20people%20reach%20out%20to%20us%20if%20they%20are%20going%20through%20something%20or%20if%20they%20know%20someone%20who%20is.%20I%20have%20also%20openly%20talked%20about%20my%20trauma%20on%20social%20media%20so%20that%20more%20women%20speak%20up.%20This%20has%20helped%20and%20I%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20requests%20for%20help%20through%20Instagram%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevanshi%20says%20the%20initial%20step%20when%20a%20victim%20approaches%20them%20is%20to%20ensure%20their%20comfort.%20%E2%80%9CI%20talk%20to%20them%20and%20listen%20to%20their%20concerns.%20Then%2C%20we%20tell%20them%20how%20they%20can%20take%20legal%20action%20against%20their%20perpetrators.%20Many%20need%20therapy%20and%20counselling%20too%2C%20so%20we%20refer%20them%20to%20our%20volunteers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevanshi%20says%20th